      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds good. I want to make sure the \"economic necessity\" part is really strong. Can you expand on that section? Like, what are the most undeniable reasons why just saying \"work harder\" or \"meritocracy\" doesn't work for people of color, and why redistribution is the only logical solution?",
